flowchart LR
    TRIGGER([Trigger])
    TRIGGER_NOTE[/Schedule, push, Figma webhook, or manual/]
    AUDIT[Sync audit]
    AUDIT_NOTE[/Diff Figma components vs codebase components/]
    CLASSIFY{Classify delta}
    N_FIGMA[New in Figma only]
    N_CODE[New in code only]
    DRIFT[Changed on both sides]
    INSYNC[Already in sync]
    CHANGED_FIGMA[Figma updated]
    CHANGED_CODE[Code updated]
    RESOLVE{Resolve conflict}
    RESOLVE_NOTE[/Human decides source of truth/]
    SCAFFOLD[[Scaffold component from Figma]]
    SCAFFOLD_NOTE[/Claude API + Figma REST + design tokens/]
    GEN_MAP[[Generate Code Connect mapping]]
    GEN_MAP_NOTE[/Claude API + ts-morph AST + Figma spec/]
    UPDATE_COMP[[Update component from Figma diff]]
    UPDATE_MAP[[Update existing mapping file]]
    TS_CHECK{TypeScript valid?}
    SELF_FIX[[Self-correct via Claude]]
    VISUAL_CHECK{Visual match?}
    VISUAL_FIX[[Regenerate mapping]]
    PUBLISH[[Publish batch to MCP]]
    CHROMATIC{Visual regression pass?}
    PR[Open PR with full diff]
    Q([Merge and sync complete])

    TRIGGER -->|note| TRIGGER_NOTE
    TRIGGER --> AUDIT
    AUDIT -->|note| AUDIT_NOTE
    AUDIT --> CLASSIFY
    CLASSIFY -->|new in Figma| N_FIGMA
    CLASSIFY -->|new in code| N_CODE
    CLASSIFY -->|both changed| DRIFT
    CLASSIFY -->|no change| INSYNC
    CLASSIFY -->|Figma changed| CHANGED_FIGMA
    CLASSIFY -->|code changed| CHANGED_CODE
    DRIFT --> RESOLVE
    RESOLVE -->|note| RESOLVE_NOTE
    RESOLVE -->|Figma wins| CHANGED_FIGMA
    RESOLVE -->|code wins| CHANGED_CODE
    N_FIGMA --> SCAFFOLD
    SCAFFOLD -->|note| SCAFFOLD_NOTE
    CHANGED_FIGMA --> SCAFFOLD
    N_CODE --> GEN_MAP
    GEN_MAP -->|note| GEN_MAP_NOTE
    CHANGED_CODE --> UPDATE_MAP
    UPDATE_MAP --> TS_CHECK
    SCAFFOLD --> GEN_MAP
    GEN_MAP --> TS_CHECK
    TS_CHECK -->|fail| SELF_FIX
    SELF_FIX --> TS_CHECK
    TS_CHECK -->|pass| VISUAL_CHECK
    VISUAL_CHECK -->|fail| VISUAL_FIX
    VISUAL_FIX --> VISUAL_CHECK
    VISUAL_CHECK -->|pass| PUBLISH
    UPDATE_COMP --> TS_CHECK
    CHANGED_FIGMA --> UPDATE_COMP
    INSYNC --> PUBLISH
    PUBLISH --> CHROMATIC
    CHROMATIC -->|fail| PR
    CHROMATIC -->|pass| PR
    PR --> Q
